-- | The resulting contexts and roles are fully integrated in the sense of the five
-- | basic responsibilities of the PDR:
-- | PERSISTENCE
-- | SYNCHRONISATION
-- | RULE TRIGGERING
-- | QUERY UPDATES
-- | CURRENTUSER

